### Ask Mimo Chatbot
POST http://localhost:3000/mimo/chatbot
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Who is Mimo?"
}

### Add a custom question and answer to Mimo
POST http://localhost:3000/mimo/customize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is a new question?",
  "answer": "This is the custom answer."
}